&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Qualified Accountant (ACA or ACCA), preferably trained within a Big 4 or Top 10 accounting practice environment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3 years PQE with strong technical accounting and financial reporting experience under IFRS.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience working in industry for a private equity backed or multinational environment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Consolidation experience.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ability to develop cross-functional relationships.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to identify areas for improvement and best in class practice.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
